Meet <b>Nickole</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Nickole lives at <a href='/home/?user=carina409'>47607 Breeze Street</a>, on the edge of the forest in Golden Valley.  She has been exploring the woods and hills around her neighborhood since moving there on August 5, 2005, and she's loved watching the seasons change.<br><br>What makes Nickole unique is how caring she is.  She's always ready to help someone in need, especially an animal.  Nickole loves to volunteer at animal shelters, and she often takes dogs and cats to visit sick or elderly people at nursing homes.  She enjoys brightening other people's days.  Nickole's caring nature, when added to her charm, makes her a wonderful friend, and her popularity among the students at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a> shows how much she is valued for her special qualities.<br><br>Nickole is also quite athletic and loves to spend time with her friends in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park/">Peabody Park</a>, playing baseball, basketball, or hockey.  Though she usually prefers team sports, Nickole also enjoys figure skating from time to time.  When she doesn't have her hockey skates on, she usually has her figure skating boots laced up.  Nickole likes to express herself artistically through the use of graceful body movements, but she enjoys the athletic challenge of skating as well.  She can often be seen gliding across <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/pond/">Peabody Pond</a> during the winter, wearing one of her beautiful gold, silver, and violet costumes.<br><br>When she wants to relax, Nickole usually heads to the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/theater.phtml">movie theater</a> at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Downtown Entertainment Complex</a>.  She finds that sitting in a dark theater and enjoying a good movie with a bucket of popcorn is the best way for her to unwind after a long day at school or on the playing field.  Nickole also likes to hang out at a mall with her friends and check into all of the latest disco, rap, and pop CDs, or browse the newest fashions for something to wear.<br><br>Thank you for being a fine citizen, Nickole, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
